<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>hk - About</title>
    <%- include('./partials/theme-head') %>
</head>

<body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <%- include('./partials/header') %>

    <main class="flex-grow mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16 py-10">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
                <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-wide mb-8">Our Story</h1>
                <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    Launced in 2015, HK is South Asia’s premier online shopping makterplace with an active presense in Bangladesh. Supported by wide range of tailored marketing, data and service solutions, hk has 10,500 sallers and 300 brands and serves 3 millioons customers across the region.
                </p>
                <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
                    hk has more than 1 Million products to offer, growing at a very fast. hk offers a diverse assotment in categories ranging from consumer.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 h-[500px] bg-[#E8E8E8] rounded overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573855619003-97b4799dcd8b?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="About Us">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats Section -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 my-20">
            <div class="border border-stone-300 rounded p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center cursor-pointer hover:bg-primary hover:text-white hover:border-primary transition group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-stone-300 group-hover:bg-red-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition">
                    <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-black group-hover:bg-white text-white group-hover:text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition">
                        <i class="ri-store-2-line text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">10.5k</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">Sallers active our site</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-stone-300 rounded p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center cursor-pointer hover:bg-primary hover:text-white hover:border-primary transition group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-stone-300 group-hover:bg-red-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition">
                    <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-black group-hover:bg-white text-white group-hover:text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition">
                        <i class="ri-money-dollar-circle-line text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">33k</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">Mopnthly Produduct Sale</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-stone-300 rounded p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center cursor-pointer hover:bg-primary hover:text-white hover:border-primary transition group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-stone-300 group-hover:bg-red-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition">
                    <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-black group-hover:bg-white text-white group-hover:text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition">
                        <i class="ri-shopping-bag-3-line text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">45.5k</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">Customer active in our site</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-stone-300 rounded p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center cursor-pointer hover:bg-primary hover:text-white hover:border-primary transition group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-stone-300 group-hover:bg-red-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition">
                    <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-black group-hover:bg-white text-white group-hover:text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition">
                        <i class="ri-money-dollar-box-line text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">25k</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">Anual gross sale in our site</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service Features -->
        <section class="mt-32 mb-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-10 md:gap-20">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center max-w-xs">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-stone-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <i class="ri-truck-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">FREE AND FAST DELIVERY</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Free delivery for all orders over $140</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center max-w-xs">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-stone-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <i class="ri-customer-service-2-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">24/7 CUSTOMER SERVICE</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Friendly 24/7 customer support</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center max-w-xs">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-stone-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <i class="ri-shield-check-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">MONEY BACK GUARANTEE</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">We return money within 30 days</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>
